></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uez1665703545897.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uez1665703545897.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uez1665703545897\" role=\"article\">\n<p class=\"shortdesc\">An <code class=\"ph codeph\">area frame</code> that defines logical unit in a form or report\n      component. It can be used to format data, or add and protect text.</p>\n\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nlv1665703545404.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>area frame</a><p>A development object that can be used to group, separate, or decorate the contents of a form or report component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xth1665703546134.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>form</a><p>An interactive component that enables users to view, create, and modify data in a Windows or character-based application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/flc1665703546204.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>report</a><p>A Uniface presentation component that defines the content and layout of printed output of a Uniface application. It can be run locally or remotely, but it cannot be displayed on screen, or update the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbac